Description: Have you ever swiped up on the entry field bar's quick compose camera icon only to mistakenly take & send a picture? ...If so then this is for you. Have you ever swiped up on the entry field bar's quick compose camera icon only to mistakenly take & send a picture? ...If so then this is for you.
 .
 When sliding up, this makes the camera icon require a separate tap before actually sending a picture.
 .
 [v.1] Tested on iP6+ 8.1 & 8.4.  (9-5-15)
